bool operator==(const mapping<OtherExtents>& m) const;
```

* *Constraints:* `OtherExtents::rank()` equals `rank()`.

* *Returns:* `true` if and only if for 0  `r` < `rank()`,
    `m.extent(r)` equals `extent(r)` and
    `m.stride(r)` equals `stride(r)`.

```c++
