stride(typename Extents::size_type r) const noexcept;
```

* *Returns:*

    * If `StorageOrder` is `column_major_t`, `stride_` if `r` equals 1, else 1;

    * else, if `StorageOrder` is `row_major_t`, `stride_` if `r` equals 0, else 1.

```c++
